---
title: Vegan Coconut-Ginger Noodle Soup with Sweet Potatoes, Snow Peas & Crispy Onions
description: Noodles. Veggies. Crispy fried onions. If you’re looking for a quick, warming vegan dinner idea, look no further! Here, you’ll sauté sweet potatoes with ginger and garlic, then add crisp snow peas, luscious coconut milk, and chewy quick-cooking ramen noodles. Top with a scattering of fresh cilantro and crispy fried onions, and finish with a bright squeeze of lime juice for a colorful, comforting bowl in just 30 minutes.
